install/ setup tailwind css (node should be install in Windows)
          1)open tailwind official side in google =>
          2)for npm "installnpm install -D tailwindcss"
          3)npx tailwindcss init
          4)crete input.css 
          5)npx tailwindcss -i ./src/main/resources/static/css/input.css -o ./src/main/resources/static/css/output.css --watch
          
